'''T'bac''' was a mild drug that was [[Smoking/Legends|smoked]].<ref name="XWING">''[[X-Wing: The Bacta War]]''</ref> [[Anzat (species)|Anzati]] [[Assassin/Legends|assassin]] [[Dannik Jerriko]] enjoyed smoking t'bac.<ref name="CCG-Jerriko">{{CCG|set=A New Hope Limited|cardname=Dannik Jerriko}}</ref> T'bac farming was a common occupation among the [[Yarkora/Legends|Yarkora]] species.<ref name="CCG-Yarkora">{{CCG|set=Jabba's Palace Limited|cardname=Yarkora}}</ref>

